------------------------------------------------
Ahmed    | Desert   | 12 Mar | Pending | Deposit
John     | Quad     | 12 Mar | Confirmed | Paid
```

---

## Features

* filters:

  * date
  * status
  * activity

* quick actions:

  * confirm
  * cancel
  * edit

